    "description": "<strong>Welcome to the Cambrian Dawn!</strong><br><br>Cambrian Dawn features a plethora of colorful and well researched species: <br>from Parvibellus to Omnidens, there are many characters to choose from.<br><br>Hunt, Swim, and Explore through the shallows, venture into the abyss, or journey to the grand sponge reefs where the fight for survival is always present!<br><br>Cambrian Dawn features a unique take on the prehistoric genre with a focus on the Cambrian Period of earth's history.<br><br>Explore the Cambrian like never before!<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br>Over 40 base-game playable species<br>AI creatures that populate the world around you.<br>Casual growth system.<br>Basic combat system. <br>Private matches with the ability to invite friends via Steam.<br>Active support on the forums.<br>Living Encyclopedia with narrated species entries.<br><br>Trailer Music:<br><i>Junkyard Tribe</i> by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 license.<br><br><strong>NOTICE:</strong> <br>Contains bright/flashing colors on some creatures, as well as mild blood.",
